ActInvestment Canada Act
SubjectNational Security Review of Investments Regulations
PrecisNATIONAL SECURITY REVIEW OF INVESTMENTS REGULATIONS is to prescribe time periods for the government to conduct national security review, as well as provide a list of investigative bodies with which confidential information can be shared and used for the purposes of their investigations.
